snippet.title: Paper Mario: TTYD Hero Mode (Demo v3.1) - [#9]
snippet.description:
What a sloppy fight... So many bad plays... 😅
------------------------------------------------------
🎮The Version I'm playing on: Hero Mode v3.1 🎮 
------------------------------------------------------
Want to play Hero Mode for yourself? Join the Paper Mario Modding discord and look for the hero-mode channel: https://discord.gg/xbszxgH
Want to know even more about Hero Mode? Go to the Github: https://github.com/Reeds-github/Hero-Mode
------------------------------------------------------
📺 TeamCamCrew: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCShVN5FnAR6c1brr-AacAMQ
------------------------------------------------------
🟣 Twitch - CleverFox64
https://www.twitch.tv/cleverfox64

🐤 Twitter - @Slyfox_64
https://twitter.com/Slyfox_64

📷 Instagram - 06jamie04
https://www.instagram.com/06jamie04/?hl=en
▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬
0:00 - Talking to the locals in Petalburg
3:38 - Quick Shopping #1
4:09 - Getting the Items where the red blocks were! #1 (Ether Flower)
4:19 - Peach E-mail (✉)
4:59 - Battle! (Enemy having the Hold Fast Badge!)
6:03 - Getting the Items where the red blocks were! #2 (Mini-Mushroom)
6:07 - Getting the Items where the red blocks were! #3 (Volt Shroom)
6:16 - Looking at the new items
6:40 - Quick Shopping #2
7:21 - Star Cookie (1st Shop Reward)
7:45 - Going back...
8:18 - Electro Blooper
20:08 - Going to the thousand-year door
22:15 - Frankly Shenanigans
23:35 - Tattle Log
23:54 - Checking out the new shop!
25:19 - Checking out the Badge Shop!
26:13 - Charlieton
26:44 - Outro (Bye-Bye)
▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬
